    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >深入航空事故的隐秘核心，在《飞机失事模拟器：序章》中探索逼真的坠机现场，分析证据，解决谜题。揭开灾难的真相，体验完整的“飞机失事”案件。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《飞机失事模拟器：序章》中，使用先进的调查工具，沉浸在航空灾难的复杂案情中，用尖端的技术和专业的分析来破解一场飞机坠毁的谜团。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的任务是<strong>到达飞机坠毁的现场</strong>。借助<strong>无人机</strong>等工具，找到飞机残骸可能的位置,</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104670/extras/d043fb2dea020afbc65b86e58a64ff33.poster.avif?t=1728891548\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104670/extras/d043fb2dea020afbc65b86e58a64ff33.webm?t=1728891548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104670/extras/d043fb2dea020afbc65b86e58a64ff33.mp4?t=1728891548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >并<strong>调查坠机现场</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104670/extras/b57722e6118a0b0a68bbbebc9cbfc623.poster.avif?t=1728891548\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104670/extras/b57722e6118a0b0a68bbbebc9cbfc623.webm?t=1728891548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104670/extras/b57722e6118a0b0a68bbbebc9cbfc623.mp4?t=1728891548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你必须标记事故区域，<strong>寻找证据</strong>，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104670/extras/efc7a6e0b19a167075b822a07676c4b7.poster.avif?t=1728891548\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104670/extras/efc7a6e0b19a167075b822a07676c4b7.webm?t=1728891548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104670/extras/efc7a6e0b19a167075b822a07676c4b7.mp4?t=1728891548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拍下证物照片，并将整个飞机残骸运送到机库。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运送飞机残骸只是你调查的开始。要找出坠机的原因，你必须<strong>重建飞机残骸</strong>，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104670/extras/29c040d50551444abfb9ba023477532f.poster.avif?t=1728891548\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104670/extras/29c040d50551444abfb9ba023477532f.webm?t=1728891548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104670/extras/29c040d50551444abfb9ba023477532f.mp4?t=1728891548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将部件送去分析或<strong>检查黑匣子</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104670/extras/e862c0ab8933270beb5f0beaca6fd638.poster.avif?t=1728891548\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104670/extras/e862c0ab8933270beb5f0beaca6fd638.webm?t=1728891548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104670/extras/e862c0ab8933270beb5f0beaca6fd638.mp4?t=1728891548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >调查的另一个重要步骤是<strong>询问目击者</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104670/extras/c5eeca2f747d58547ef883887a5ee630.poster.avif?t=1728891548\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104670/extras/c5eeca2f747d58547ef883887a5ee630.webm?t=1728891548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104670/extras/c5eeca2f747d58547ef883887a5ee630.mp4?t=1728891548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >并收集所有的线索，以找出坠机原因的<strong>真相</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104670/extras/01debcc7bc5363c0cc7299c2e93abba1.poster.avif?t=1728891548\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104670/extras/01debcc7bc5363c0cc7299c2e93abba1.webm?t=1728891548\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2104670/extras/01debcc7bc5363c0cc7299c2e93abba1.mp4?t=1728891548\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《飞机失事模拟器：序章》中，体验诱人的神秘航空世界。但，时刻牢记，你所看到的只是冰山一角，一旦深入到完整的游戏中，你将会踏上一个充满秘密及阴谋的世界。</p>",
